Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边 不好意思啊 突然叫你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码的父亲居然会反对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要选这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着她老爹不在的时候 去说服伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母肯定会站在我们这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 日记也借给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是为了面码 她一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码 如果知道我们又瞒着她跑去她家的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 啊啦 今天集君和知利子也来了啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.06,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是火箭花火对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听她爸爸说的时候 真吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友们聚在一起 想出了这么有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的 小时候和面码约好一起做的 花火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 芽衣子她...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...放了花火的话 面码...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子也会...那个...我想她应该也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能不能和伯父...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 你们关系真的非常好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-诶?  -哪里...也没那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子应该会很羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她又被孤立了  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上说芽衣子会开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是自己找乐子吧 拿芽衣子当借口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子她...明明已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们却还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也是 你们不是和芽衣子在一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.09,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你读过那孩子的日记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就停在那一天了啊 时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那孩子还留在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么你们长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有芽衣子她...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子...一个人孤零零地...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见 你的手没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好可怕啊 面码的老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一直都对我们怀恨在心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人讨厌到这个地步 可能还是我人生中的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是父母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现面码的愿望这种荒唐的事还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊 那面码怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你也该醒醒了  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在配合你而已 配合可怜的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也做过那样的事 没资格说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 我不会像你这样想把自己的伤痛强加于人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的伤痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是这样吗 就因为你被过去束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连面码的父母都...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都受到了伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一定是在说他自己吧 雪集说的受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你哦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信面码在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-仁太?  -无所谓了 我一个人来实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不是说必须要大家一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 一直觉得大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 实际和大家聊了之后 很吃惊大家其实没怎么变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 再怎么没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的「大家」已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...少了面码
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然「大家」已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去实现也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会继续的 和之前一样 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的啊 我正脱鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有我一个人 也能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有我一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?你又增加兼职了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 干体力活工资比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色似乎不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-嗯 因为没睡  -诶?我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直以来过的都是吃了就睡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积攒了足够的睡眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能这么拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么喜欢面码吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个 营养剂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太不也受了很大伤害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样了 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这样是指什么啊  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候也是 其实不想让你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在要开始说些性格很恶劣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 其实我松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太说不喜欢面码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很差劲 不过我真的有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那样走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和你亲口说你最喜欢面码一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后一直很心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅在那一瞬间觉得开心的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了面码 还发生了那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法 无法原谅喜欢仁太的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还是...我还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说 就算面码真的在仁太那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现了愿望的话面码不就消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕面码消失啊?明明喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太这个...笨蛋!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这笨蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码 在等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲好黑 我用牙签给你弄干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你弄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 一旦愿望实现了 面码就会...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 再忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这是面码所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那么疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起<弗兰德斯的狗>了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起帕特拉修来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕特拉修?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰德斯的...以前...重播时候看的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么啊 这谎撒得太烂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!我觉得帕特拉修一定是很幸福的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为尼洛对它那么那么好 而且还和它做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了面码之后 面码的母亲一直对我们怀恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru一直在责备自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子肯定也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连波波也...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在罪恶感中得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到面码
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我被面码拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么不公平...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个时间了 今天打工...啊 去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要去学校?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是塔子的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 等我下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我在下边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我自己能看到面码的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有必须为面码实现愿望的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不去学校 老爸也从来没有说过我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为他是对我死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...可是...所谓的父母...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我说啊...  -嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打工的事你不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?你知道的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 啊 对了 是去本间先生家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是在说哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我什么都不知道哦  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...我都不知道仁太想为什么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 把香拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真斗不过父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太居然连早上好都没说就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?啊咧?是波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算面码的老妈是那种态度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能全都让仁太自己做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为超和平busters好不容易又和以前一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.36,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.46,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们吵架了吗? 为什么波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 面码的事我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有仁太看得到 别人都不信 我也信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?诶?无言电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 呐 宿海应该是在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号码显示是宿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海打来的无言电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一些很刷拉刷拉就像沙暴一样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说可能你会觉得我傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会不是宿海打来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 安城居然不请假就不来上班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有听安城说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真是倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本来打算和拳击俱乐部的朋友一起开PARTY的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.84,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(本店无法使用信用卡)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我该怎么见anaru啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 该道歉的是我们这些不速之客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的父母都不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大妈 基本不出家门的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不想见到别人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我明白姐姐去世了她很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 让人觉得很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人是自己的母亲 都觉得有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得他们最辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓父母 怎么说呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些话我不配说...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有一个活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我还很小 对姐姐几乎没有什么记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一些事我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪君不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉你哦 姐姐啊 可是超和平busters  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去保卫大家的和平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以聪君要保护好我们的家 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我保护家...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那种阴沉沉的家...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 仁太也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?怎么都来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天去干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?打工...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话 不是你吗 打到我们家里的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点多的时候打到我家的 无言电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无言?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非怎么说 你又要把面码抬出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个时间我和老爸都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能真的是面码...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么玩意儿啊你 面码面码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样让我也看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码不是在吗 那让我也看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 别冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 不要再玩这个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了 宿海 这种时候还玩面码的幽灵游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在吗 仁太 面码在那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要添乱了 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托了 拜托了 不要再这样了  -诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对面码做的事永远都无法改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码怎么可能会道歉 面码怎么可能会原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...又没有风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 到底为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和长大的大家一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秘密基地玩...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超和平busters永远都是好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是面码的字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 正解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面码...为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:22:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是面码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯...